show.description: On a luxury getaway, a wealthy couple is falsely accused of fraud, facing humiliation at the hands of a ruthless resort manager. But when their true identity is revealed, the tables turn in a storm of justice and reckoning. A gripping drama of respect, power, and karma—proving dignity is priceless. Watch now!
